description: This request is for the acquisition of a new dropping point apparatus, which will replace an old aging system that is no longer supported. The new dropping point apparatus will provide clients with service in a timely manner. The dropping point system DP70 is to support the Information, Science, and Technology branch and maintain the sections’ capabilities at Canada Border Services Agency (CBSA). Item Quantity1.
